; Golden Test: Medium Pipeline (100 rows)
; Tests: weekday filter on financial data
; Expected runtime: <2 seconds
; This exercises:
; - file: CSV loading (100 rows, 2 columns: TIMESTAMP, GC1 Comdty)
; - wkd: weekday (Mon-Fri) filter (removes Sat/Sun, outputs ~70 rows)
; - NA handling: preserves NA values in output
;
; This validates:
; 1. CSV I/O works correctly
; 2. Weekday filter correctly identifies and removes weekend rows
; 3. Date range: 2000-01-01 to 2000-05-XX (100 calendar days, ~70 weekdays)
; 4. NA values are preserved through the pipeline

(-> (file "data/gld_num_mini/GC1C_100.csv")
    (wkd))
